}

###

### 66. Ver carrito de c2 inicial ($25)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{customerId2}} HTTP/1.1

###

### 67. Agregar p1 a c2 para alcanzar mínimo
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/add-product HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "{{customerId2}}",
  "productId": "{{productId1}}"
}

###

### 68. Ver carrito de c2 (ahora con $1025)
# p1 (Laptop $1000) + p2 (Mouse $25) = $1025
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart/{{customerId2}} HTTP/1.1

###

### 69. Aplicar cupón 20% ahora que cumple mínimo
# Mínimo: $500 ✓ (cumple con $1025)
# Descuento: 20% de $1025 = $205
# Total esperado: $820
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart/apply-coupon HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "{{customerId2}}",
  "couponCode": "{{coupon20}}"
}

